Heng Xin Says Tao Chi Keung Resigned as Chief Financial Officer

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-10-11T10:24:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/heng-xin-says-tao-chi-keung-resigned-as-chief-financial-officer.html
Heng Xin China Holdings Ltd. (8046)  Chief
Financial Officer Tao Chi Keung resigned due to “career
change,” the company said in a statement to the Hong Kong stock
exchange today.  The company didn’t have a disagreement with Tao, it said.  Tao was appointed CFO on July 18, according to a July 19
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Lui at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net  